snippet.title: The Frostrune Pre-Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more at: http://www.thefrostrune.com

Explore an authentic mysterious Norse environment through The Frostrune, a point-and-click adventure game, to unravel a mystery inspired by Viking myths and legends. The Frostrune is made by game developers who are passionate and schooled in Norse mythology and history. We have taken extra care to make The Frostrune as authentic and historically accurate as possible. 

Follow the Frostrune: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/grimnirmedia
Twitter: https://twitter.com/grimnirmedia
Website: http://www.thefrostrune.com
